<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="184" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1227,2107,766,1390]" pageId="0" pageNumber="184">• Small to medium-sized prosimians with highly developed, elongated hindlimbs, generally short snout, round eyes, large, naked, membranous, mobile ears, large, soft, woolly fur, and long, usually thick tail.</paragraph>
