<paragraph blockId="0.[1227,2107,766,1390]" pageId="0" pageNumber="184">• Tropical lowland, swamp, riparian, montane, and submontane forests and forest-edge, thicket and scrub, hilly and semi-arid woodlands, savanna, and tree plantations.</paragraph>
